    <a class="js-post-issue flex--item s-btn s-btn__unset c-pointer py6 mx-auto" href="/posts/27823412/timeline" data-shortcut="T" data-ks-title="timeline" data-controller="s-tooltip" data-s-tooltip-placement="right" aria-label="Timeline" aria-describedby="--stacks-s-tooltip-m6vpx1kq"><svg aria-hidden="true" class="mln2 mr0 svg-icon iconHistory" width="19" height="18" viewbox="0 0 19 18"><path d="M3 9a8 8 0 1 1 3.73 6.77L8.2 14.3A6 6 0 1 0 5 9l3.01-.01-4 4-4-4zm7-4h1.01L11 9.36l3.22 2.1-.6.93L10 10z"/></svg></a><div id="--stacks-s-tooltip-m6vpx1kq" class="s-popover s-popover__tooltip" role="tooltip">Show activity on this post.<div class="s-popover--arrow"/></div>

</div>

            </div>

            

<div class="answercell post-layout--right">
        <div class="js-endorsements" data-for-answer="27823412">
</div>

    
    <div class="s-prose js-post-body" itemprop="text">
<p>You can do it with <a href="https://github.com/letsdrink/ouzo-goodies" rel="nofollow">ouzo goodies</a>:</p>

<pre class="lang-php s-code-block"><code data-highlighted="yes" class="hljs language-php"><span class="hljs-variable">$result</span> = <span class="hljs-title class_">Arrays</span>::<span class="hljs-title function_ invoke__">sort</span>(<span class="hljs-variable">$restrictedEvents</span>, <span class="hljs-title class_">Comparator</span>::<span class="hljs-title function_ invoke__">compareBy</span>(<span class="hljs-string">'title'</span>));
</code></pre>

<p><a href="http://ouzo.readthedocs.org/en/latest/utils/comparators.html" rel="nofollow">http://ouzo.readthedocs.org/en/latest/utils/comparators.html</a></p>
    </div>
