    <div class="s-prose js-post-body" itemprop="text">
<p>Usually something like this is achieved via a second array with <code>$keyToSort =&gt; $id</code>, sort this array via the standart sort functions or your own, then you have a conversion to your first array</p>

<p>using this, the depth of your array is limitless.</p>
